org.openehealth.ipf.commons.ihe.xds.core.ebxml

Interface EbXMLProvideAndRegisterDocumentSetRequest

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EbXMLObjectContainer, EbXMLSubmitObjectsRequest
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EbXMLProvideAndRegisterDocumentSetRequest21, EbXMLProvideAndRegisterDocumentSetRequest30

    public interface EbXMLProvideAndRegisterDocumentSetRequest
extends EbXMLSubmitObjectsRequest
    Encapsulation of the ebXML classes for ProvideAndRegisterDocumentSetRequestType.

    This class contains convenience methods and provides a version independent abstraction of the ebXML data structure.

    Author:
    Jens Riemschneider
